OL,6,FA critical incident has been declared
OL,7,Fby Hampshire Hospitals NHS Foundation
OL,8,FTrust, which runs hospitals in
OL,9,FBasingstoke and Winchester.
OL,11,FBeds at the Royal Hampshire County
OL,12,FHospital and Basingstoke and North
OL,13,FHampshire Hospital are full and
OL,14,Fattendance at emergency departments is
OL,15,Fhigh.
OL,17,FIn a statement, the Trust announced
OL,18,Fthere is no capacity to admit further
OL,19,Fpatients.
