OL,3,CCritical incident declared at
OL,4,CBasingstoke and Winchester hospitals
OL,6,FA high admission rate, a high number
OL,7,Fof infectious patients needing
OL,8,Fisolation and a low discharge rate are
OL,9,Fsaid to be contributing to "sustained
OL,10,Fpressures".
OL,12,FThe Trust is urging people to only
OL,13,Fattend A&E for a life-threatening
OL,14,Fillness or injury. Anyone collecting a
OL,15,Ffriend or loved one is being asked to
OL,16,Fdo so at the earliest opportunity.
OL,18,FThose with non-urgent and non-life-
OL,19,Fthreatening conditions are being asked
OL,20,Fto contact NHS 111, GPs, pharmacies or
OL,21,Furgent treatment centres.
