OL,3,CCritical incident declared at
OL,4,CBasingstoke and Winchester hospitals
OL,6,FJulie Dawes, chief nurse for Hampshire
OL,7,FHospitals, said: "There are two ways
OL,8,Fthe public can help at this time:
OL,9,Ffirstly, by only attending our
OL,10,FEmergency Departments if acutely
OL,11,Funwell or injured; and secondly by
OL,12,Fcollecting loved ones who are ready
OL,13,Ffor discharge.
OL,15,F"A considerable number of beds are
OL,16,Fbeing used to care for individuals who
OL,17,Fwould be more comfortable recuperating
OL,18,Fin a home setting.
